name: hand knitted iphone & ipod case 1
description:
Protect your iphone and ipod with this hand knitted case!

Made from 100% Merino wool

Beautiful Liberty fabric lines the case, with tweed piping and pretty buttons adding detail to the front.

Great for:

iphone 3G
iphone 3Gs
ipod
ipod touch

Width: 7cm
Length: 10cm
